description:
Only the notes in the arpeggiated chords in the first half of the song for Seth's parts were incorrect. If you watch a playthrough of their songs and watch covers they are all played this way. I am very attatched to this song so I just wanted to help. I also added the youtube video and can be used as reference as well. Thank you so much for the consideration and have been using the app since 2011!
(via editor)
title: Ov My Herculean Exile
